-- New Oriental Drops Most in Three Months on Sales Outlook
-- B y   B e l i n d a   C a o
-- 2012-01-17T15:11:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-17/new-oriental-drops-most-in-three-months-on-sales-outlook.html
  New Oriental Education & Technology
Group Inc. ,  China ’s largest private education service provider,
plunged the most in three months after its sales forecast for
the quarter ended in February fell short of of analysts’
estimates.  The American depositary receipts of the Beijing-based
company sank 10 percent to $22.79 at 10:06 a.m. New York time,
the biggest intraday slump since Oct. 18.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Belinda Cao in New York at 
